SALESFOURCE RELEASE NOTES

Supercharge Product Browsing Experience for Your Partners and Customers

You can now add the Product List, Product Details, Product Attribute Details, and Product Bundle Details components to Experience Cloud site pages. 

Partners and customers can use these components to browse catalogs, categories, and products in a simple, structured way to identify the most suitable products. They can get a single, comprehensive view of product information using the Product Details, Product Attribute Details, and Product Bundle Details components.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

How: Open an Experience Cloud site page in Experience Builder, click Components, and then drag components to the canvas.
title: Supercharge Product Browsing Experience for Partners and Customers
